OL,3,CVal Kilmer: Top Gun and Batman actor
OL,4,Cdies aged 65
OL,6,FTop Gun star Val Kilmer has died at
OL,7,Fthe age of 65, his daughter has said.
OL,9,FKilmer's daughter Mercedes told the
OL,10,FNew York Times the actor had died from
OL,11,Fpneumonia.
OL,13,FHe rose to fame starring alongside Tom
OL,14,FCruise in the 1986 hit Top Gun.
OL,16,FKilmer would go on to play Batman in
OL,17,F1995's Batman Forever and received
OL,18,Fcritical acclaim for his portrayal of
OL,19,Fmusician Jim Morrison in the 1991 film
OL,20,FThe Doors.
