OL,4,Cdies aged 65
OL,6,FKilmer's final acting role was a cameo
OL,7,Fin the 2022 blockbuster sequel Top
OL,8,FGun: Maverick.
OL,10,F"I just want to say that was pretty
OL,11,Femotional," Tom Cruise told Jimmy
OL,12,FKimmel in 2023 about the cameo.
OL,14,F"I've known Val for decades, and for
OL,15,Fhim to come back and play that
OL,16,Fcharacter... he's such a powerful
OL,17,Factor that he instantly became that
OL,18,Fcharacter again."
