OL,6,FHe underwent both radiotherapy and
OL,7,Fchemotherapy, as well as a
OL,8,Ftracheostomy, which damaged his vocal
OL,9,Fcords.
OL,11,F"I obviously am sounding much worse
OL,12,Fthan I feel," Kilmer said in the
OL,13,Fdocumentary.
OL,15,F"I can't speak without plugging this
OL,16,Fhole (in his throat). You have to make
OL,17,Fthe choice to breathe or to eat.
OL,19,F"It's an obstacle that is very present
OL,20,Fwith whoever sees me."
