OL,3,CVal Kilmer: Top Gun and Batman actor
OL,4,Cdies aged 65
OL,6,FIn a post on Instagram, actor Josh Gad
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to the action star.
OL,9,FHe said: "RIP Val Kilmer. Thank you
OL,10,Ffor defining so many of the movies of
OL,11,Fmy childhood. You truly were an icon."
OL,13,FActor Josh Brolin, son of James
OL,14,FBrolin, said he was going to miss his
OL,15,F"pal".
OL,17,F"You were a smart, challenging, brave,
OL,18,Fuber-creative firecracker," he said in
OL,19,Fan Instagram post.
