OL,6,F"There's not a lot left of those. I
OL,7,Fhope to see you up there in the
OL,8,Fheavens when I eventually get there.
OL,9,FUntil then, amazing memories, lovely
OL,10,Fthoughts."
OL,12,FKilmer married British actress Joanne
OL,13,FWhalley in 1988, whom he met while
OL,14,Fworking on the film Willow.
OL,16,FThe couple had two children before
OL,17,Fdivorcing in 1996.
